Language name: MURSI
Language number: 4214
Alternate names: Murle
Classification: Nilo-Saharan, E. Sudanic
Comments: The language is tonal but the system is not well 
understood.
Sources: 

Arensen,  J. 1982. Murle Grammar. Occasional Papers in the 
Study of Sudanese Languages, no. 2.

Turton, D. and Bender, M.L. 1976. Mursi. In M.L. Bender 
(ed.), The Non-Semitic Languages of Ethiopia. African 
Studies Center, Michigan State University, East Lansing: 
533-62.